'''Malawi Police Service''' ndi chiwalo palokha wa wamkulu amene analamula malamulo kuteteza Zachitetezo ndi ufulu wa anthu ku Malawi .  [[Malawi]] Police Service imayang'aniridwa ndi [[Inspector General of Police]] .
